title: Google\Cloud\Dialogflow\V2\Participant
name: Participant
description:
Represents a conversation participant (human agent, virtual agent, end-user).

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.dialogflow.v2.Participant

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.name
params.description: Optional. The unique identifier of this participant. Format: projects/<Project ID>/locations/<Location ID>/conversations/<Conversation ID>/participants/<Participant ID>.

params.name: data.role
params.description: Immutable. The role this participant plays in the conversation. This field must be set during participant creation and is then immutable.

params.name: data.sip_recording_media_label
params.description: Optional. Label applied to streams representing this participant in SIPREC XML metadata and SDP. This is used to assign transcriptions from that media stream to this participant. This field can be updated.
